{"type": "article", "id": 16478, "title": "卓锦万代兰系GEL-Lyte III", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-23T06:40:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606145647OAr2sHaGp5wZ9BU6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这双鞋是 Limited Edt 和 ASICS Tiger 联合打造的限量款 GEL-Lyte III，为了庆祝新加坡建国 50 周年，特意用了新加坡的国花卓锦万代兰（Vanda Miss Joaquim）。紫、粉、红这样在球鞋上少见的鲜艳颜色搭配在一起，很特别也很大胆。此外，配合这双鞋还赠一条花卉领带、紫色鞋带和有特殊标志的清洁剂，完全是礼盒的包装。售价 195 美元。近期会在线上发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143733lhkEKPiILBCeVM7X.jpg\" width=\"440\" height=\"293\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66590909\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143734F6LiDYxQyTSlJXg8.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"652\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69361702\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143734IoEPGrilkV0pJNya.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"651\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69255319\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143735pB5RNa7DqmKP0h9Y.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}